Welcome to the Beacon Project.

To set up the project for development, do the following:

1) Install IntelliJ IDEA
2) Install Scala and SBT
3) Install IntelliJ Scala plugin
4) In IntelliJ, select "New Project" -> "From Existing Sources"
5) Select "Import project from external model" and "SBT"
6) Click through the menu, and the project should build in a minute or two

To run the Ansible playbook
ansible-playbook project-deployment.yml